On March 25, the new property management company and the property management committee of Tianzeyuan Community, Chunhua Street, Jiangning District, Nanjing City were blocked from entering the site for handover, which attracted a large number of owners to watch
It is reported that the community had legally selected a new property management company for the community in January 2022. On the morning of March 25, the new property management company and the property management committee were blocked from entering the site for handover. After the old property management company called the police, the local police station dispatched police to order the new property management company to leave the community, which caused dissatisfaction among a large number of owners. During this period, the new and old property management companies and owners confronted each other for a long time.
